Welcome to LONDYNWORLD! Happy 3rd Birthday to my baby Londyn! We were finally able to have a party for him (pandemic baby), it just took 3 years LOL! Celebrated this past Saturday, March 18th with family and friends, at his first official birthday party. Special thanks to Anthony/Court 16 for hosting us, all the kids had a fantastic time! The venue was beautiful, spacious and clean. I wanted to play some tennis too but was too busy hosting. We had yummy mini cupcakes which were perfect for little fingers from Baked by Melissa and guests of Londyn left with epic favors: Vans Lunch Sacks, Honest Kids Bath + Body products and Court 16 x Babolat Rackets! Lastly, I want to thank everyone that came to celebrate with my lil man! Until next time‚Ä¶
